            <title>联想 YOGA Pad Pro 平板磁吸键盘及支架开售：配 AI 功能键，699 元</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/817/264.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/817/264.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 15:26:57 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1431819" rel="nofollow">花花蚣子</a> 的线索投递！</div>
            <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 12 月 12 日消息，联想于 12 月 11 日宣布 YOGA Pad Pro 平板配套磁吸键盘及支架、磁吸保护夹、钢化膜已经开售，价格分别为 699 元、149 元以及 69 元。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="967" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/12/74b7a84b-44e1-4162-8b4e-42312796fdf5.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xZC9xZDIyMi5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_22,x_22,a_0/format,f_auto" title="联想 YOGA Pad Pro 平板磁吸键盘及支架开售：配 AI 功能键，699 元" width="1440" /></p><p>YOGA Pad Pro 磁吸键盘及支架提供雾海蓝、浅海贝两款配色，物理连接一贴即合，支持 120°-160° 无极调节。键盘配备<strong> 1.5mm 键程、16 个直观功能键、62mm*105mm 触控板</strong>，此外还有一颗专属 AI 功能键，一键即可唤出联想小天。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="973" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/12/3e48d0a8-d3f6-449c-bf3b-55c6853b972a.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 YOGA Pad Pro 平板磁吸键盘及支架开售：配 AI 功能键，699 元" width="1440" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="967" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/12/cc6cf460-f8db-4bf2-819a-98228db16d8a.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想 YOGA Pad Pro 平板磁吸键盘及支架开售：配 AI 功能键，699 元" width="1440" /></p><p>磁吸保护夹采用高规格 PU 材质打造，背板翻折即可为平板竖起三角支架，翻盖即可点亮屏幕，合盖自动休眠；钢化膜为 0.25 高透高铝玻璃材质，2.5D 边缘弧度处理。</p><p>IT之家获悉，联想手写笔 Pro 此前已经单独上市销售，售价 599 元。联想&nbsp;YOGA Pad Pro AI&nbsp;元启版平板<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/814/706.htm" target="_blank">已于&nbsp;12&nbsp;月&nbsp;2&nbsp;日开售</a>，<strong>该款平板搭载骁龙&nbsp;8 Gen3&nbsp;处理器</strong>、配备&nbsp;2.9K 144Hz&nbsp;刷新率显示屏，售价&nbsp;3299&nbsp;元起。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="453" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/12/ddb5c992-7ec2-4f96-831f-fa6675c09eda.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xZC9xZDEzNy5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_14,x_14,a_0/format,f_auto" title="联想 YOGA Pad Pro 平板磁吸键盘及支架开售：配 AI 功能键，699 元" width="889" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/u1U6NLY" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/221244/14/48564/57374/6746ea7bFbfbe603f/2fb5c0aa3ac941b0.png" title="联想 YOGA Pad Pro 平板磁吸键盘及支架开售：配 AI 功能键，699 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">联想 YOGA Pad Pro 磁吸键盘及支架</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 699 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/uGUyo2o" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/197357/33/50931/14292/6746de29F4aa39007/9bdc8401771f0a59.png" title="联想 YOGA Pad Pro 平板磁吸键盘及支架开售：配 AI 功能键，699 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">联想 YOGA Pad Pro 磁吸保护夹</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 149 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/u1U1CFS" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/184807/37/54098/59280/6746e1f3Fc4484ec4/7f2f2c3b5a5ff1bd.png" title="联想 YOGA Pad Pro 平板磁吸键盘及支架开售：配 AI 功能键，699 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">联想 YOGA Pad Pro 钢化膜</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 69 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
